Song 085 The Old Settler's Song
This song that we're singing's a story.
It happened to you and to me.
It started a-round nineteen-sixty, and may last 'til nineteen-ninety-three.

Back then we had many computers, from STRETCH to the fourteen-oh-one,
with so many different instructions, we all could have oodles of fun.

But I-B-M wanted new profits, and a product con-sis-tency.
So they designed System three-sixty as an arch-i-tecture fam-ily.

Three-sixty had many instructions,
that were to remember too hard.
So ol' I-B-M went and printed a multi-page green reference card.
chorus
