Notes
1 Houston Automatic Spooling Package (HASP)
2 Job Entry Subsystem 2              (JES2)
3 System generation                  (SYSGEN)
4 Initial Program Load               (IPL)
5 VS = Virtual System
6 RJE = Remote Job Entry
7 CPU = Central Processing Unit
8 CRT = Cathode Ray Tube
9 DBA = Data Base Administrator
10 IMS = Information Management System
11 1401 = second generation machine
12 370 = third generation machine
13 Abend F03
14 Type 3 software supplied by IBM on an AS IS basis
15 CTC = channel-to-channel
16 UP = uniprocessor (a single processor)
17 AP = attached processor
18 MVS = multiple virtual system
19 FE = field engineer
20 JQE = job queue element (JES2)
21 JCT = job control table (JES2)
22 SRB = supervisor request block
23 DCB = data control block
24 TCB = task control block
25 IOT = input/output table
26 UCB = unit control block
27 IOB = input/output block
28 DEB = data event block
29 CVT = communications vector table
30 MP = multiprocessor
